info.description:
Provides connectivity to SAP using the new SAP NW RFC SDK.  The NW RFC SDK (from
SAP)
supersedes the older RFC SDK, and will ultimately be nolonger maintained - this also
applies to the old saprfc connector (http://cheeseshop.python.org/pypi/saprfc/)
which will become progressively out of date as SAP retires the old RFC SDK.
info.name: sapnwrfc
